---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="How It Works — AI Employee Deployment in 3 Steps | Amoris"
  description="From discovery call to live AI employee in 3–4 weeks. See exactly how Amoris scopes, builds, and deploys AI employees for your business."
>

<section style="padding-bottom:40px;">
  <span class="section-eyebrow reveal">Process</span>
  <h1 class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:16px; max-width:20ch;">Hired and working in 3–4 weeks.</h1>
  <p class="reveal" style="max-width:52ch; font-size:1.05rem;">No lengthy discovery. No 6-month implementations. One problem, one AI employee, live in weeks.</p>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:0;">
  <div class="steps-grid stagger-cards">
    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-n">01</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:16px;">Book a Demo Call</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">30 minutes. Tell us your biggest time-drain or missed-revenue problem. We map it to a specific AI employee and give you a ballpark scope and cost on the call.</p>
      <div class="step-outputs">
        <div class="step-output-label">What you leave with</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Specific AI employee recommendation</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Rough scope and price range</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Clear next steps if you want to proceed</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-card">
      <div class="step-n">02</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:16px;">We Build & Deploy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">After you sign, we get to work. Integration setup, AI training on your data, testing with real scenarios, and then deployment. You review and approve before it goes live.</p>
      <div class="step-outputs">
        <div class="step-output-label">What happens in this phase</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Integration with your existing tools</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Training on your specific data and scripts</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Testing with real scenarios from your business</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Your approval before going live</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-card step-card-gold">
      <div class="step-n step-n-gold">03</div>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem; margin-bottom:16px;">It Works. You Grow.</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">Your AI employee handles the work 24/7. We monitor it, improve it monthly, and expand it as your needs grow. You focus on what only humans can do.</p>
      <div class="step-outputs">
        <div class="step-output-label">What ongoing looks like</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Monthly performance reviews</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Knowledge base updates as your business changes</div>
        <div class="step-output">✓ Expansion to additional AI employees when ready</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="border-top:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="hiw-network-section reveal">
    <div>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Integration</span>
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Connects to the tools you already use.</h2>
      <p style="max-width:44ch; margin-bottom:28px;">We don't replace your stack. Your AI employee plugs into WhatsApp, CRM, calendar, email, and wherever your business runs — reading and writing just like a human employee would.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px;">
        {['WhatsApp', 'Gmail', 'Google Calendar', 'HubSpot', 'Zoho CRM', 'Salesforce', 'Notion', 'Google Sheets', 'Slack', 'Zoom', 'Freshdesk', 'Razorpay'].map(tool => (
          <span class="tag">{tool}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg class="network-svg-large" viewBox="0 0 320 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="160" cy="160" r="44" fill="rgba(240,168,36,0.08)" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.3)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="160" y="155" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Space Grotesk, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#F5F3EE">Amoris</text>
      <text x="160" y="172" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#F0A824">AI OS</text>
      <circle cx="160" cy="160" r="110" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,6"/>
      <line x1="160" y1="116" x2="160" y2="58" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="2s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="160" cy="46" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="160" y="43" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">💬</text>
      <text x="160" y="57" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">WhatsApp</text>
      <line x1="191" y1="135" x2="238" y2="92" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="2.4s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="252" cy="80" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="252" y="77" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">📧</text>
      <text x="252" y="91" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">Gmail</text>
      <line x1="204" y1="160" x2="262" y2="160" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="1.8s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="276" cy="160" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="276" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">🗂️</text>
      <text x="276" y="171" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">CRM</text>
      <line x1="191" y1="185" x2="238" y2="228" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="2.2s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="252" cy="242" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="252" y="239" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">📅</text>
      <text x="252" y="253" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">Calendar</text>
      <line x1="129" y1="185" x2="82" y2="228" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="2.6s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="68" cy="242" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="68" y="239" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">📊</text>
      <text x="68" y="253" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">Sheets</text>
      <line x1="116" y1="160" x2="58" y2="160" stroke="rgba(240,168,36,0.2)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,4"><animate attributeName="stroke-dashoffset" from="0" to="-14" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite"/></line>
      <circle cx="44" cy="160" r="24" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#26262A" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="44" y="157" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14">💼</text>
      <text x="44" y="171" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="7" fill="#9B9891">Slack</text>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="border-top:1px solid var(--border); text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute; left:50%; top:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:500px; height:200px; background:radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(240,168,36,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events:none;"></div>
  <div style="position:relative; z-index:1;">
    <h2 class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:12px;">Start the process.</h2>
    <p class="reveal" style="max-width:40ch; margin:0 auto 32px;">Book a 30-minute demo call. Tell us the problem. We'll tell you which AI employee solves it.</p>
    <div class="reveal" style="display:flex; gap:14px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Demo →</a>
      <a href="/ai-employees" class="btn btn-outline">Browse AI Employees →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.steps-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }
@media (max-width:900px) { .steps-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
.step-card { background:var(--bg-raised); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:36px; }
.step-card-gold { border-color:rgba(240,168,36,0.25); }
.step-n { font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:11px; color:var(--text-muted); background:var(--bg-inset); border:1px solid var(--border); width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:24px; }
.step-n-gold { color:var(--gold); background:var(--gold-dim); border-color:rgba(240,168,36,0.25); }
.step-outputs { background:var(--bg-inset); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); padding:16px; margin-top:4px; }
.step-output-label { font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:10px; }
.step-output { font-size:13px; color:var(--text-dim); padding:4px 0; }
.hiw-network-section { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:60px; align-items:center; }
@media (max-width:900px) { .hiw-network-section { grid-template-columns:1fr; } }
.network-svg-large { width:100%; max-width:320px; display:block; margin:0 auto; }
</style>
</Base>
